@node SETSTYLETAGNAME

@{U}@{FG Highlight}SETSTYLETAGNAME                                                             @{FG Text}@{UU}

Purpose: Changes the name of a style tag.

Syntax:  @{b}setstyletagname@{ub} <newstylename/S> [STYLETAG name/S]

Format:  @{U}Parameter@{UU}  @{U}Values to enter@{UU}
         stylename  is the new name of the style tag.
         STYLETAG   is the current name of the style tag.

Example: setstyletagname 'Body Text' styletag 'paragraph text'

